==English==
===Etymology===
From the past participle stem of Latin [[nictitare]], frequentative form of [[nictare]] ‘wink’ (see English [[nictate]]).

===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /'nɪktɪteɪtɪŋ/

===Adjective===
{{en-ad|nictitating}}
# [[winking]], [[blinking]]

===Verb===
'''nictitating'''
* present participle of [[nictitate]]